Class FileSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileSystem
  • public class FileSystem
extends java.lang.Object
    FileSystem class represents a file system. It provides functionality for managing directories and files.

      • search

        public FileSystemElement search​(java.lang.String name,

        name - The name of the element to search for.
        directory - The directory to search within.
